OL,3,C'I had 17 calls in one hour, it was
OL,4,Cscary': the patients without a voice
OL,6,FA mother and daughter from Ukraine
OL,7,Fhave described how "scary" language
OL,8,Fbarriers in healthcare in Wales can be.
OL,10,FOlga Bakar and her mother Vira have
OL,11,Flived in Wales UK for less than 2
OL,12,Fyears after leaving Ukraine due to the
OL,13,Fwar.
OL,15,FLast year, Vira needed a triple heart
OL,16,Fbypass and whilst she doesn't speak
OL,17,FEnglish, thankfully her daughter Olga
OL,18,Fdoes and was able to help translate
OL,19,Fwhile Vira was in hospital.
