OL,3,C'I had 17 calls in one hour, it was
OL,4,Cscary': the patients without a voice
OL,6,F"Sometimes she wasn't able to explain
OL,7,Fwhat she needs," said Olga.
OL,9,F"Sometimes if they brought her a menu,
OL,10,Fshe wouldn't be able to use it, she
OL,11,Fwouldn't be able to select something
OL,12,Fbecause she simply didn't know what to
OL,13,Fsay.
OL,15,F"It was so scary because if my mum was
OL,16,Fnot able to communicate with someone,
OL,17,Feven for a very minor issue, she'd
OL,18,Fcall my phone. I had 17 calls in one
OL,19,Fhour, so to see so many calls was so
OL,20,Fscary."
