OL,3,C'I had 17 calls in one hour, it was
OL,4,Cscary': the patients without a voice
OL,6,FShe said she felt like her mother
OL,7,F"wasn't helpless because she had me
OL,8,Fand my son (her grandson). We tried to
OL,9,Freplace each other and provide her
OL,10,Fwith the best support we can.
OL,12,F"We split our duties and we try to
OL,13,Fmonitor my mum. We tried to make it as
OL,14,Fsmooth as possible with our limited
OL,15,Flanguage capacities. We tried to read
OL,16,Fabout her cardiac problems."
