OL,6,FVira added: "It's (NHS) such a good
OL,7,Fservice, it's got such a good level of
OL,8,Fhealthcare, but she couldn't imagine
OL,9,Fhow difficult it is for people who
OL,10,Faren't able to talk.
OL,12,FIt comes as a Senedd report recommends
OL,13,Ftranslators are provided to patients
OL,14,Fto help avoid health conditions being
OL,15,Fmissed.
