OL,3,C'I had 17 calls in one hour, it was
OL,4,Cscary': the patients without a voice
OL,6,F"I suspected something wasn't getting
OL,7,Facross so I suggested a perineal
OL,8,Fexamination. That revealed that she
OL,9,Fhad cervical cancer and when I
OL,10,Freferred her as USC (urgent suspected
OL,11,Fcancer) it came back as stage 4.
OL,13,F"That's one example of something that,
OL,14,Fwith better translation support, we
OL,15,Fcould have possibly picked up earlier.
OL,16,FBecause of the communication issue, it
OL,17,Fwas missed."
