OL,3,C'I had 17 calls in one hour, it was
OL,4,Cscary': the patients without a voice
OL,6,F"We come across many times people who
OL,7,Frequire extra support in terms of
OL,8,Flanguage and needing a professional
OL,9,Ftranslator and then you end up picking
OL,10,Fup things that can be quite worrying
OL,11,Fbecause it wasn't picked up earlier."
OL,13,FJenny Rathbone MS, Chair of the
OL,14,FEquality and Social Justice Committee
OL,15,Fsaid it shows there is more to be done
OL,16,Fbefore Wales can become an anti-racist
OL,17,Fnation.
