OL,6,FA Welsh Government spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"We welcome the Committee's report and
OL,8,Fwill carefully consider their
OL,9,Frecommendations.
OL,11,F"We are committed to driving forward
OL,12,Four Anti-racist Wales Action Plan and
OL,13,Fworking towards achieving an anti-
OL,14,Fracist Wales by 2030. We recognise the
OL,15,Fimportance of reducing instances where
OL,16,Ffamily members are acting as
OL,17,Finterpreters.
